N-Butanol is a versatile chemical compound that finds applications in various industries such as automotive, chemicals, and paints & coatings. The market for N-Butanol is driven by its use as a solvent in paints and coatings, as well as in the production of chemicals and plastics. The increasing demand for N-Butanol in the automotive industry for manufacturing adhesives, sealants, and coatings is also fueling market growth. Additionally, the growing construction industry is contributing to the rise in demand for N-Butanol for use in coatings and adhesives. The rising focus on sustainable manufacturing practices and the shift towards bio-based N-Butanol production are expected to create new opportunities in the market.

